specific%20recipes%20after%20you%20complete%20the%20questionnaire.%20Instead%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20up%20to%20three%20of%20the%20five%20recipes.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20individual%20ingredients%20cannot%20be%20added%20or%20removed%20from%20the%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelivery%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDelivery%20days%20vary%20by%20zip%20code.%20You%20can%20usually%20choose%20from%20four%20different%20delivery%20days.%20You%20can%20also%20add%20delivery%20instructions%20if%20you'd%20like%20the%20food%20left%20somewhere%20other%20than%20your%20front%20door%2C%20such%20as%20your%20back%20door%20or%20garage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPackaging%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Pets%20Table%20ships%20its%20frozen%20meals%20in%20vacuum-sealed%20plastic%20bags%20packed%20in%20a%20cardboard%20box%20insulated%20with%20dry%20ice.%20Trial%20boxes%20include%20a%20reusable%20container%20for%20storing%20thawed%20food%20in%20the%20fridge.%20Food%20should%20be%20kept%20in%20the%20freezer%20until%20you're%20ready%20to%20thaw%20and%20serve%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22077b3219-3f6f-44a1-bba7-8a33fc176bd7%5C%22%3EOur%20review%20of%20The%20Pets%20Table%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20placing%20my%20order%2C%20The%20Pets%20Table%20sent%20frequent%20notifications%20about%20shipment%20and%20delivery%20status%2C%20both%20of%20which%20I%20could%20also%20track%20from%20my%20website%20account%20page.%20While%20this%20level%20of%20communication%20is%20standard%20among%20the%20brands%20I've%20tested%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20valuable%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20trial%20box%20of%20The%20Pets%20Table%20fresh%20dog%20food%20is%20displayed%20on%20a%20table%20and%20includes%20a%20food%20storage%20container%2C%20bandana%2C%20and%20three%20packages%20of%20dog%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c1ac485e81483682cbc5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20first%20box%20from%20The%20Pets%20Table%20included%20two%20weeks%20of%20food%2C%20a%20reusable%20storage%20container%2C%20a%20cute%20bandana%2C%20and%20complementary%20treats.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20arrived%20in%20a%20cardboard%20box%20packed%20with%20dry%20ice%20that%20kept%20it%20frozen%20solid.%20I've%20gone%20back%20and%20forth%20on%20whether%20I%20prefer%20dry%20ice%20or%20ice%20packs%20for%20fresh%20dog%20food%20deliveries%2C%20but%20ultimately%20I've%20landed%20on%20dry%20ice%20as%20the%20better%20option.%20I%20try%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20waste%20by%20reusing%20ice%20packs%2C%20but%20finding%20space%20in%20my%20freezer%20gets%20tough%20as%20orders%20stack%20up.%20The%20Pets%20Table%20also%20includes%20a%20few%20extras%20in%20your%20trial%20box%3A%20a%20storage%20container%20for%20thawed%20food%2C%20a%20feeding%20guide%2C%20a%20bandana%2C%20and%20a%20sample%20bag%20of%20treats%20for%20your%20pup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnpacking%20my%20order%20was%20a%20breeze%20thanks%20to%20the%20smart%20packaging%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20pro%20for%20me.%20The%20food%20comes%20in%20long%2C%20rectangular%20bags%20that%20lie%20flat%20in%20the%20freezer%2C%20making%20them%20easy%20to%20stack%20and%20helping%20conserve%20valuable%20freezer%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20contents%20of%20an%20open%20box%20are%20shown%20from%20above%20and%20they%20contain%20pouches%20of%20frozen%20fresh%20dog%20food%20from%20The%20Pets%20Table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c27adf748d8c055f45720%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20food%20arrived%20completely%20frozen%20and%20neatly%20packaged.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feeding%20guide%20included%20in%20the%20box%20provides%20thawing%20and%20serving%20instructions.%20After%20thawing%20the%20food%20in%20the%20refrigerator%20(at%20least%2012%20hours%20before%20serving)%2C%20I%20simply%20cut%20open%20the%20bag%20and%20followed%20the%20measurement%20directions.%20Lyla's%20included%20feeding%20guide%20said%20she%20should%20eat%20one%20bag%20per%20day.%20This%20recommendation%20was%20fine%2C%20according%20to%20both%20her%20veterinarian%20and%20her%20appetite.%20For%20pet%20parents%20with%20dogs%20that%20require%20smaller%20portions%2C%20the%20measurements%20printed%20on%20the%20bag%20will%20be%20especially%20useful.%20Any%20leftover%20food%20went%20into%20the%20provided%20storage%20container%20to%20save%20for%20the%20next%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20tried%20some%20fresh%20foods%20in%20the%20past%20that%20had%20a%20strong%20odor%2C%20but%20The%20Pets%20Table%20had%20virtually%20no%20smell.%20What%20I%20did%20smell%20of%20the%20food%20was%20pleasant%2C%20even%20when%20the%20food%20was%20leftover%20from%20the%20day%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20composite%20of%20a%20hand%20holding%20a%20pouch%20of%20The%20Pets%20Table%20Turkey%20Casserole%20beside%20a%20bowl%20containing%20the%20same%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c26e03d5881a51c1c0f1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Turkey%20Casserole%20With%20Broccoli%20includes%20chickpeas%2C%20sweet%20potatoes%2C%20carrots%2C%20spinach%2C%20and%20salmon%20oil.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20convenient%20packaging%20and%20feeding%20instructions%2C%20Lyla%20was%2C%20unsurprisingly%2C%20far%20more%20interested%20in%20the%20food.%20With%20most%20dog%20food%20brands%2C%20she%20tends%20to%20lose%20interest%20after%20a%20few%20weeks.%20But%20during%20our%20monthlong%20trial%20with%20The%20Pets%20Table%2C%20she%20ate%20every%20single%20meal%20without%20hesitation.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20picky%20eater%2C%20you'll%20understand%20my%20joy%20when%20she%20polished%20off%20each%20bowl%20twice%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyla%20enjoyed%20all%20three%20of%20the%20recipes%20we%20tried%3A%20the%20Chicken%20Casserole%2C%20Turkey%20Casserole%2C%20and%20Beef%20Stew.%20I%20eventually%20stopped%20feeding%20her%20the%20Beef%20Stew%20due%20to%20some%20slight%20stomach%20upset%2C%20but%20even%20that%20didn't%20deter%20her%20from%20coming%20back%20for%20more%20of%20The%20Pets%20Table.%20If%20your%20dog%20has%20food%20sensitivities%2C%20you%20can%20easily%20review%20the%20full%20ingredient%20lists%20for%20each%20recipe%20on%20The%20Pets%20Table%20website.%20However%2C%20you%20should%20consult%20your%20vet%20if%20you're%20unsure%20what%20may%20be%20causing%20your%20pet%20to%20have%20frequent%20stomach%20upset%2C%20as%20there%20may%20be%20a%20variety%20of%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0011a13-20cc-41c7-80a2-ae9185ffcd40%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20kibble%20or%20even%20canned%20food%2C%20fresh%20dog%20food%20isn't%20exactly%20budget-friendly.%20For%20this%20review%2C%20I%20was%20given%20a%20complimentary%20month%20of%20food%2C%20but%20had%20I%20subscribed%20myself%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20about%20%24145%20for%20two%20weeks%20of%20meals%2C%20plus%20%2410.99%20shipping.%20While%20The%20Pets%20Table%20is%20more%20affordable%20than%20some%20other%20fresh%20dog%20food%20delivery%20services%2C%20it's%20still%20more%20expensive%20than%20Lyla's%20usual%20rotation%20kibble%20and%20wet%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubscribers%20can%20swap%20recipes%20before%20delivery%2C%20but%20individual%20ingredients%20can't%20be%20customized.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20scheduling%20delivery%2C%20The%20Pets%20Table%20also%20doesn't%20offer%20as%20much%20flexibility%20as%20other%20brands.%20You%20can%20choose%20the%20delivery%20date%20and%20pause%20or%20skip%20shipments%2C%20but%20The%20Pets%20Table%20determines%20your%20delivery%20frequency%2C%20which%20can%20range%20from%20two%20to%20eight%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20other%20drawback%20is%20the%20limited%20availability%20of%20grain-inclusive%20recipes.%20Currently%2C%20The%20Pets%20Table%20offers%20just%20two%20grain-inclusive%20recipes%2C%20which%20were%20added%20shortly%20after%20I%20began%20testing.%20While%20my%20veterinarian%20and%20I%20determined%20that%20a%20grain-free%20diet%20is%20fine%20for%20my%20pup%2C%20that%20might%20not%20be%20the%20case%20for%20all%20dogs.%20It's%20best%20to%20consult%20your%20vet%2C%20who%20can%20determine%20the%20best%20diet%20to%20keep%20your%20four-legged%20friend%20healthy%20and%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227e18fa9-fa1f-4eda-ac4d-4013da819423%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20my%20picky%20dog%20liked%20The%20Pets%20Table%20%E2%80%94%20she%20enjoyed%20the%20flavor%20of%20all%20three%20recipes%20she%20tried.%20I%20also%20appreciated%20the%20simple%20ordering%20process%20and%20the%20convenient%20packaging.%20While%20it's%20not%20the%20most%20customizable%20option%20for%20fresh%20dog%20food%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20choice%20if%20you%20value%20a%20no-fuss%2C%20straightforward%20approach%20to%20feeding%20your%20pet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets-table-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750883244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c43be85e81483682cc12a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets-table-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pets%20Table%20is%20a%20fresh%20dog%20food%20delivery%20service%20from%20HelloFresh.%20I%20tested%20it%20for%20a%20month%20and%20found%20many%20pros%20plus%20a%20few%20cons%20to%20consider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.c