.com%2Fapple-advertising-google-search-services-filings-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebusiness%20for%20Apple%20one%20day%20%E2%80%94%20part%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bservices%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20push%20it%20has%20been%20on%20as%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-earnings-service-growth-iphone-drop-antitrust-google-app-store-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EiPhone%20sales%20plateau%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20theories%20are%20starting%20to%20make%20a%20bit%20more%20sense%20now%20that%20Apple%20seems%20to%20be%20gaining%20some%20buzz%20around%20some%20of%20its%20TV%20shows%20%E2%80%94%20though%20its%20streaming%20service%20still%20doesn't%20have%20anything%20like%20the%20reach%20of%20Netflix%2C%20Disney%2C%20or%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseverance-apple-tv-how-many-watch-chart-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Apple's%20approach%20to%20movie-making%20remains%20as%20confusing%20as%20ever.%20Up%20until%20recently%2C%20Apple%20was%20spending%20lots%20of%20money%20on%20all%20kinds%20of%20movies%2C%20and%20it%20was%20unclear%20what%20it%20was%20getting%20out%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8af3bd02af33dea8c804640ce377ba95eb86ef5cf75f5bbc10f5b37deba947c3%26postID%3D685c4c0e68e21fcf0f194e82%26postSlug%3Dwhy-does-apple-make-movies-f1-brad-pitt-2025-06%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.apple.com%252Fnewsroom%252F2022%252F03%252Fapples-coda-wins-historic-oscar-for-best-picture-at-the-academy-awards%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20did%20grab%20an%20Oscar%20for%20%26quot%3BCoda%26quot%3B%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20thing%20lots%20of%20streamers%20would%20love%20to%20have%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20of%20its%20other%20movies%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BNapoleon%2C%26quot%3B%20have%20gotten%20respectful%20notices%20fr