0cost%20a%20couple%20of%20bucks%20more%20than%20they%20would%20normally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20seemed%20somewhat%20callous%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ehe%3C%2Fem%3E%20should%20try%20telling%20that%20to%20a%20little%20kid%20on%20Christmas%20morning.%20But%20frankly%2C%20something%20about%20this%20stirred%20something%20deep%20inside%20me.%20Yes%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20I%20would%20prefer%20if%20my%20daughter%20had%20fewer%20dolls%20because%20her%20toy%20box%20is%20overflowing%20with%20dolls%2C%20and%20it%20stresses%20me%20out.%20Personally%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20mind%20if%20there%20were%20significantly%20fewer%20toys%20in%20my%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToys%20are%20an%20interesting%20category%20in%20terms%20of%20inflation%2C%20and%20something%20I'm%20slightly%20obsessed%20with%20(not%20just%20because%20I%20often%20look%20at%20my%20living%20room%20and%20wish%20the%20toy%20mess%20of%20my%20two%20kids%20and%20feel%20despair).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwENbN9eLUVI%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Cheap%20Toys%20Made%20Millennial%20Parents%20Miserable%20%7C%20Business%20Insider%20Explains%20%7C%20Insider%20News%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20back%20on%20my%20childhood%20in%20the%20'80s%20and%20'90s%2C%20and%20toys%20seemed%20(in%20my%20child%20mind)%20so%20much%20more%20expensive%20than%20they%20do%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20toys%20have%20seen%20significant%20price%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Edeflation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20over%20the%20last%2030%20years.%20Basically%2C%20a%20toy%20that%20cost%20your%20parents%20%2420%20in%201993%20would%20only%20cost%20you%20around%20%24