f%20Kid%20Cudi's%20car%20after%20it%20was%20firebombed%20in%20his%20Hollywood%20Hills%20driveway%20in%202011.%3Cp%3EUS%20Attorney's%20Office%2C%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20fuck%2C%26quot%3B%20Mescudi%20said%20with%20an%20embarrassed%20smile%20when%20asked%20by%20the%20prosecution%20to%20describe%20his%20reaction%20to%20seeing%20his%20torched%20car%20in%20the%20driveway%20of%20his%20Hollywood%20Hills%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20cross-examination%2C%20Mescudi%20said%20he%20had%20no%20direct%20knowledge%20that%20anyone%20affiliated%20with%20Combs%20was%20involved%20with%20the%20never-solved%20arson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deep%20cut%20to%20the%20list%20of%20racketeering%20activities%20leaves%20the%20indictment%20listing%20six%20alleged%20racketeering%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20bribery%2C%20tampering%20with%20witnesses%2C%20forced%20labor%2C%20transportation%20for%20purposes%20of%20prostitution%2C%20inducement%20for%20purposes%20of%20prostitution%2C%20and%20distributing%20and%20possessing%20narcotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJurors%20must%20come%20to%20a%20unanimous%20agreement%20on%20two%20crimes%20on%20that%20list%2C%20finding%20that%20Combs%20and%20others%20in%20his%20music%20and%20lifestyle%20company%2C%20Combs%20Global%2C%20agreed%20to%20commit%20those%20crimes%20as%20part%20of%20a%20pattern%20of%20racketeering%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20follow%20arguments%20in%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20during%20which%20Combs'%20attorney%20Alexandra%20Shapiro%20described%20the%20weaknesses%20that%20defense%20lawyers%20see%20in%20the%20prosecution's%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20elements%20of%20the%20racketeering%20conspiracy%20charged%20in%20the%20indictment%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20began.%20Racketeering%20conspiracy%20carries%20a%20potential%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20life%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%2C%20at%20best%2C%20thin%20proof%20that%20any%20of%20the%20other%20employees%20knowingly%20participated%20in%20the%20crimes%20with%2C%20or%20for%2C%20Mr.%20Combs%2C%20other%20than%20things%20like%20picking%20up%20or%20helping%20Mr.%20Combs%20procure%20personal%20use%20quantities%20of%20drugs%20for%20himself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20scant%20evidence%20showing%20that%20employees%20knowingly%20agreed%20with%20Combs%20to%20commit%20crimes%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20testimony%20about%20the%20employees%20shows%20that%20they%20ran%20errands%20related%20to%20his%20personal%20life%2C%20made%20travel%20arrangements%20for%20him%20and%20his%20girlfriends%2C%20and%20the%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20then%20picked%20apart%20the%20underlying%20crimes%2C%20one%20by%20one%2C%20including%20the%20kidnapping%2C%20arson%2C%20and%20sex-trafficking%20crimes%20that%20prosecutors%20edited%20from%20the%20indictment%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20there%20was%20no%20direct%20evidence%20linking%20Combs%20to%20the%20arson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221154%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Molotov%20cocktail%20thrown%20in%20Kid%20Cudi's%20car%20in%20Beverly%20Hills%20in%202011.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c3ac1f748d8c055f45940%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22860%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Molotov%20cocktail%20thrown%20in%20Kid%20Cudi's%20car%20Beverly%20Hills%20in%202011.%3Cp%3EUS%20Attorney's%20Office%2C%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20Capricorn%20Clark%20nor%20Cassie%20Ventura%20nor%20Mr.%20Mescudi%20witnessed%20the%20arson%20or%20put%20Mr.%20Combs%20at%20Mr.%20Mescudi's%20residence%20at%20the%20relevant%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20sex-trafficking%2C%20there%20was%20likewise%20no%20proof%20that%20Combs'%20employees%20believed%20anything%20illegal%20might%20have%20been%20going%20on%20with%20Ventura%20and%20%26quot%3BJane%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20second%20sex-trafficking%20accuser%2C%20Shapiro%20argued.%20So%20there%20was%20no%20proof%20of%20an%20enterprise%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%26quot%3Bracket%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20aiding%20in%20sex%20trafficking%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20also%20criticized%20the%20government's%20kidnapping%20accusations%2C%20which%20allege%20in%20part%20that%20Combs%20forced%20Clark%2C%20his%20former%20executive%2C%20to%20go%20to%20Mescudi's%20house%20to%20%26quot%3Bkill%26quot%3B%20him.%20The%20defense%20has%20argued%20that%20while%20Combs%20may%20have%20had%20a%20gun%2C%20it%20was%20never%20pointed%20at%20Clark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25983671-us-v-combs-us-racketeering-edits-20250625%2F%3Fembed%3D1%26height%3D600%26title%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-prosecutors-drop-kid-cudi-allegations-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750874278000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f7d2bca50259add4cd48f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-prosecutors-drop-kid-cudi-allegations-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kid%20Cudi%20may%20have%20testified%20for%20nothing.%20Prosecutors%20no%20longer%20care%20about%20kidnapping%20and%20car%20arson%20allegations%20relating%20to%20his%20romance%20with%20Cassie.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A104%2C%22c