3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20healthcare%20facilities%20can%20prepare%20their%20data%20for%20AI-assisted%20contract%20management%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nurse%20at%20the%20computer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685aeaca3d5881a51c1bfe39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3Eultramarinfoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHealthcare%20companies%20are%20increasingly%20using%20AI%20for%20tasks%20like%20contract%20review%20and%20management.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProper%20data%20preparation%20is%20crucial%20for%20effective%20AI%20implementation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-everything-supply-chain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20Is%20Changing%20Everything%3A%20Supply%20Chain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20on%20innovations%20in%20logistics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20healthcare%2C%20pharmaceutical%2C%20and%20medical-technology%20companies%20have%20focused%20the%20bulk%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharmaceutical-companies-embrace-ai-in-drug-discovery-efforts-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20investments%20on%20clinical%20uses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20AI%20has%20been%20employed%20to%20help%20diagnose%20breast%20cancer%2C%20identify%20potential%20patients%20for%20clinical%20trials%2C%20and%20accelerate%20the%20processes%20used%20to%20determine%20whether%20a%20device%20or%20a%20new%20drug%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20work%20or%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20medical%20centers%20are%20investing%20in%20AI%20for%20backend%20uses%2C%20such%20as%20speeding%20up%20contract%20generation%2C%20management%2C%20and%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%20effectively%2C%20companies%20should%20structure%20their%20data%20for%20AI-powered%20analysis%2C%20said%20David%20Gould%2C%20the%20chief%20customer%20officer%20at%20EncompaaS%2C%20a%20technology%20company%20that%20helps%20organizations%20prepare%20their%20data%20for%20implementing%20AI%20tools.%20Company%20leaders%20should%20also%20recognize%20that%20adopting%20AI%20is%20a%20continuous%20process%20that%20requires%20investing%20in%20employee%20upskilling%2C%20healthcare%20supply%20chain%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22636f0b24-3eb2-4891-8844-b72c662dc0b7%5C%22%3EPrepare%20data%20for%20effective%20and%20accurate%20algorithm%20input%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECreating%20uniform%20data%20sets%20is%20an%20essential%20step%20for%20any%20organization%20seeking%20to%20build%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ai-dictionary-help-understand-nvidia-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elarge%20language%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20deploy%20an%20effective%20chatbot%2C%20Gould%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20data%20that's%20used%20to%20train%20any%20given%20LLM%20has%20to%20be%20accurately%20classified%20or%20organized%20into%20a%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStructured%20data%2C%20by%20its%20nature%2C%20is%20classified%2C%26quot%3B%20Gould%20said.%20This%20includes%20information%20that's%20already%20in%20a%20healthcare%20system's%20database%2C%20like%20customer%20ID%20numbers%2C%20diagnostic%20codes%2C%20and%20prices%20for%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unstructured%20data%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20trove%20of%20PDFs%20outlining%20contracts%2C%20for%20instance%20%E2%80%94%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20properly%20prepared%20so%20that%20an%20AI%20algorithm%20knows%20which%20information%20to%20extract%20and%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20contracts%20from%20different%20vendors%20aren't%20written%20with%20a%20uniform%20structure%2C%20a%20person%20has%20to%20train%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-machine-learning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emachine-learning%20AI%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20look%20for%20specific%20things%20if%20they%20want%20to%20extract%20necessary%20data%20from%20a%20specific%20table%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20said%20Gould.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%20a%20PDF%20that's%20a%20contract.%20AI%20software%20%26quot%3Bcan%20only%20tell%20you%20that%20it's%20a%20document%20%E2%80%94%20it%20doesn't%20tell%20you%20what%20that%20context%20is%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20contract%2C%20an%20amendment%2C%20or%20a%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20Gould%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20algorithm%20only%20works%20well%20if%20the%20data%20matches%20what%20the%20algorithm%20is%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSaying%2C%20'OK%2C%20chatbot%2C%20look%20all%20across%20my%20enterprise%20for%20information%20and%20see%20what%20you%20can%20find'%20is%20not%20effective%2C%20because%20the%20processing%20cost%20is%20going%20to%20become%20very%2C%20very%20expensive.%20And%20that's%20where%20you%20get%20drift%20and%20bias%2C%20because%20the%20data%20is%20not%20really%20ready.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreparing%20data%20may%20also%20mean%20reckoning%20with%20historical%20information%20that%20wasn't%20properly%20classified%20or%20recorded%2C%20and%20ensuring%20that%20it's%20updated%20with%20the%20correct%20metadata%20for%20AI-based%20analysis.%20That%20can%20be%20time-consuming%2C%20Gould%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20data%20needs%20to%20be%20classified%20correctly%20and%20also%20within%20the%20appropriate%20context.%20That%20might%20mean%20identifying%20and%20fixing%20documents'%20previously%20mistaken%20tags.%20The%20data%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20stored%20in%20a%20way%20that%20maintains%20compliance%20with%20privacy%20and%20other%20safety%20regulations%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fwhat-is-hipaa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHIPAA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20protects%20patient%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c15bae2a-d215-4aaa-a242-e8147fb8c37b%5C%22%3EConsider%20the%20impacts%20on%20personnel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAutomating%20laborious%20manual%20tasks%20can%20be%20transformative%2C%20particularly%20for%20roles%20in%20procurement%20and%20compliance%2C%20said%20Matt%20Parker%20and%20Jacob%20Thompson%20of%20SpendMend%2C%20an%20AI%20tool%20for%20pharmacy%20procurement%2C%20at%20a%20recent%20webinar%20on%20AI%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20world%20of%20pharma%20and%20healthcare%2C%20the%20people%20that%20are%20being%20asked%20to%20do%20this%20work%20are%20highly%20educated%2C%20expensive%2C%20and%20ambitious%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gould.%20Yet%20they%20have%20historically%20been%20tasked%20with%20%26quot%3Bcutting%20and%20pasting%20of%20spreadsheet%20contracts%20to%20spreadsheets%26quot%3B%20for%20many%20hours%20a%20day.%20By%20automating%20these%20tasks%2C%20AI%20implementation%20can%20cut%20down%20on%20hours%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20employees%20may%20need%20retraining%20or%20additional%20training%20because%20AI%20often%20changes%20job%20functions%2C%20Jeremy%20Strong%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20supply%20chain%20at%20Rush%20University%20Medical%20Center%2C%20told%20BI.%20Ensuring%20there's%20a%20plan%20in%20place%20to%20address%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperiment-with-ai-tools-to-upskill-employees-says-google-researcher-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20upskilling%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20acknowledging%20the%20significance%20of%20changes%20to%20employees'%20job%20functions%20can%20help%20to%20manage%20the%20transition%2C%20Strong%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20better%20employees%20get%20at%20asking%20precise%20questions%2C%20the%20more%20AI%20algorithms%20can%20improve%20at%20providing%20accurate%20answers%2C%20said%20Gould.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20figuring%20out%20how%20many%20contracts%20with%20a%20specific%20type%20of%20clause%20will%20expire%20in%2030%20days.%20Typically%2C%20this%20process%20would%20take%20weeks%2C%20if%20not%20months%2C%20with%20a%20records%20manager%20or%20an%20entire%20records%20department%20looking%20through%20thousands%20of%20contracts.%20But%20with%20AI%2C%20an%20employee%20can%20learn%20how%20to%20ask%20a%20powerful%20and%20precise%20question%20that%20captures%20this%20information%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-healthcare-companies-can-prepare-data-for-ai-assisted-management-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750873066000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685aeaca3d5881a51c1bfe39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-healthcare-companies-can-prepare-data-for-ai-assisted-management-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20gain%20a%20competitive%20edge%20with%20AI%2C%20healthcare%20companies%20should%20reclassify%20their%20data%20in%20a%20uniform%20way%20and%20upskill%20staff%2C%20industry%20experts%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rachel%20Somerstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-healthcare-companies-can-prepare-data-for-ai-assisted-management-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20bridge%20collapse%3A%20Truck%20hangs%20mid-air%20with%20driver%20inside%20-%20watch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750872810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-122074888%2Cimgsize-4228282.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2