ealand%20as%20a%20small%20advanced%20technology%20house%20and%20launched%20our%20first%20rocket%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20raised%20our%20first%20bit%20of%20capital.%20That's%20when%20we%20started%20building%20Electron%2C%20our%20partially%20reusable%20two-stage%20rocket%2C%20and%20we're%20now%20working%20on%20Neutron%2C%20our%20medium-lift%20rocket%20scheduled%20to%20launch%20this%20year.%20The%20company%20has%20gone%20from%20generating%20a%20few%20million%20to%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20in%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20felt%20like%20a%20sprint%20pretty%20much%20the%20entire%20time.%20Here's%20a%20typical%20day%20in%20my%20life%20when%20I'm%20working%20from%20New%20Zealand%2C%20instead%20of%20traveling%20to%20our%20California%20headquarters%20or%20watching%20a%20rocket%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fcd2908-2a4c-4441-8f3e-ccf62ed18905%5C%22%3EI%20wake%20up%20between%204%3A30%20and%205%3A00%20every%20morning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frocket-lab-ceo-beck-paranoia-superpower-can-lead-to-burnout-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrible%20sleeper%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20at%20least%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20get%20out%20of%20bed%20each%20morning.%20When%20my%20body%20naturally%20wakes%20up%20between%204%3A30%20and%205%3A00%20am%2C%20I%20first%20check%20to%20see%20if%20anything%20critical%20has%20happened%20overnight%20%E2%80%94%20if%20something%20has%2C%20I'll%20head%20down%20to%20my%20office%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20wake%20my%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI's%20Power%20Hours%20series%20gives%20readers%20an%20inside%20look%20at%20how%20powerful%20leaders%20in%20business%20structure%20their%20workday.%20See%20another%20story%20from%20the%20series%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-