ing%20space%2C%20my%20desk%20got%20even%20sparser.%20I%20used%20to%20have%20a%20few%20photos%2C%20but%20now%20it's%20just%20my%20laptop%20and%20bits%20of%20rocket%20from%20old%20launches.%20Some%20are%20reminders%20of%20success%2C%20others%20reminders%20that%20this%20business%20can%20bite%20you%20in%20the%20ass%20at%20any%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20the%20rocket%20remnants%2C%20I'm%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20Post-Its.%20I%20have%20a%20row%20of%20them%20across%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20computer%20screen.%20All%20the%20way%20left%20are%20the%20most%20urgent%20problems%2C%20and%20farthest%20right%20are%20things%20I%20can%20deal%20with%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rocket%20Lab%20CEO%20Peter%20Beck%20at%20a%20launch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6859aafb3d5881a51c1be8e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeck%20keeps%20bits%20from%20old%20rockets%20on%20his%20desk.%3Cp%3ERocket%20Lab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6e2eab8-6c15-4783-9e70-1c9792bb090f%5C%22%3EI%20like%20technical%20questions%20and%20avoid%20all%20but%20the%20most%20necessary%20meetings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20there%20are%20challenges%2C%20I%20enjoy%20getting%20into%20the%20engineering%20details.%20Nowadays%2C%20I'm%20dealing%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20technical%20and%20production%20questions%20about%20Neutron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20unexpected%20moments%20are%20the%20most%20intellectually%20stimulating%20parts%20of%20each%20day.%20I%20try%20to%20avoid%20meetings%20whenever%20I%20can%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20few%20scheduled%20ones%20I%20have%20to%20attend.%20We%20have%20a%20set%20of%20rules%20in%20each%20meeting%20room%2C%20and%20if%20you're%20not%20adding%20value%2C%20you%20should%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20a%20choice%20to%20make%2C%20I'd%20much%20rather%20pull%20up%20a%20chair%20at%20someone's%20desk%20than%20call%20a%20lengthy%20group%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20take%20many%20breaks%20during%20the%20day%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20at%20work%20to%20get%20stuff%20done.%20Biology%20calls%2C%20though%2C%20and%20when%20I'm%20hungry%2C%20I'll%20go%20down%20to%20the%20cafe%20for%20lunch.%20The%20cafe%20didn't%20serve%20cake%20initially%2C%20so%20I%20mandated%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20sweet%20at%20the%20end%20of%20every%20lunch.%20Now%2C%20there's%20always%20a%20slice%20of%20cake%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20along%20with%20an%20ice%20cream%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20days%2C%20I%20try%20to%20eat%20with%20a%20random%20group%20in%20the%20cafeteria%2C%20though%20I'll%20bring%20my%20plate%20to%20my%20desk%20when%20it's%20especially%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ce4884a-0fd0-4e57-be0d-4a14ca000850%5C%22%3EI%20always%20try%20to%20make%20it%20home%20for%20family%20dinner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20leave%20the%20office%20a%20little%20bit%20after%205%20to%20get%20home%20in%20time%20for%20dinner%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20two%20teenage%20kids.%20I'm%20not%20normally%20involved%20in%20the%20cooking%2C%20which%20is%20probably%20for%20the%20best.%20We're%20all%20busy%20people%2C%20but%20there%20aren't%20excuses%20for%20skipping%20out%20on%20the%20meal%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20the%20most%20enjoyable%20part%20of%20my%20day.%20We're%20all%20jokers%2C%20so%20dinner%20often%20consists%20of%20us%20talking%20about%20our%20days%20or%20taking%20digs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20it's%20back%20to%20work.%20My%20time%20at%20home%20is%20for%20deeper%20thinking%2C%20whereas%20my%20time%20at%20the%20office%20is%20for%20solving%20practical%20problems.%20If%20I%20have%20a%20big%20choice%20to%20make%2C%20I'll%20collect%20opinions%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20then%20eventually%20sit%20down%20with%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20to%20mull%20it%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20go%20to%20sleep%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20start%20to%20get%20ineffective%2C%20which%20is%20earlier%20and%20earlier%20these%20days%2C%20typically%20around%2010%20or%2011%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217439511-46fc-42d1-b5bb-47ea9f6f321d%5C%22%3EI'm%20an%20active%20relaxer%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20include%20helicopters%20or%20race%20cars%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20consider%20myself%20an%20active%20relaxer%2C%20meaning%20I%20have%20to%20do%20an%20activity%20to%20destress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20way%20to%20active%20relax%20is%20to%20fly%20a%20helicopter.%20When%20I'm%20flying%2C%20I%20have%20to%20shut%20out%20everything%20else%2C%20or%20I%20risk%20crashing.%20I%20try%20to%20fly%20at%20least%20one%20hour%20each%20week%2C%20usually%20on%20a%20Sunday%20or%20a%20Monday.%20Occasionally%2C%20I'll%20relax%20by%20flying%20a%20jet%20or%20driving%20a%20race%20car%20%E2%80%94%20really%20anything%20where%20there's%20no%20possibility%20of%20thinking%20about%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-rocket-lab-ceo-peter-beck-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750871405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6859ab15f748d8c055f43067%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-rocket-lab-ceo-peter-beck-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Peter%20Beck%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Rocket%20Lab%2C%20doesn't%20drink%20coffee%2C%20keeps%20bits%20of%20old%20rockets%20on%20his%20desk%2C%20and%20tries%20to%20make%20it%20home%20for%20family%20dinner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22atecotzky%40businessinsider.com%20(Alice%20Tecotzky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-rocket-lab-ceo-peter-beck-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Loan%20Fraud%20Convict's%20'Catch%20Me%20If%20You%20Can'%20Of%204%20Decades%20Ends%2C%20Courtesy%20CBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22He%2