res.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20maximise%20space%2C%20Anshul%20adopted%20innovative%20techniques%20like%20wall%20farming%2C%20inspired%20by%20Israeli%20farmers%20who%20grow%20crops%20by%20creating%20multiple%20layers%20on%20walls.%20He%20creatively%20named%20his%20approach%20the%20%E2%80%98Chilaua%20Model%E2%80%99%2C%20after%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20involves%20planting%20dragon%20fruits%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20on%20overhangs%20seven%20feet%20above%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20even%20on%20terraces%2C%20effectively%20utilising%20the%20vertical%20space%20of%20a%20single%20wall.%20To%20prevent%20excessive%20weight%20on%20walls%2C%20I%20used%20thick%20plastic%20pipes%20as%20pots%2C%20planting%20two%20saplings%20in%20each%20of%20the%2050%20pots%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEfficient%20water%20management%20in%20hot%20climates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDragon%20fruit%20farming%20requires%20less%20irrigation%20compared%20to%20traditional%20crops%20like%20paddy.%20%E2%80%9CI%20irrigate%20the%20field%20once%20every%2020%20days%20in%20October%20and%20November%2C%20once%20every%2030%20days%20in%20December%20and%20January%2C%20once%20a%20week%20in%20February%20and%20March%2C%20and%20three%20times%20a%20week%20from%20April%20to%20June.%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20water%20them%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-1-1735303735.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%