%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mules%20are%20late.%20There%20is%20no%20soda%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20told.%20And%20so%20Ardeshir%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F395076%2Fferns-pickles-pune-nataline-fernandes-jams-squashes-preserves-curry-pastes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20experiment%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20would%20sate%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20soda%20appetite.%20He%20found%20a%20way%20to%20produce%20carbonated%20water.%20Soon%2C%20sugar%20and%20flavour%20found%20their%20way%20into%20the%20drink%2C%20and%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20was%20born%2C%20a%20bottled%20range%20of%20fizzy%20cheer%20that%20even%20predates%20Coca-Cola%2C%20which%2C%20by%20most%20estimates%2C%20was%20invented%20in%201886%20%E2%80%94%20two%20years%20after%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20started%20in%201884%20in%20a%20small%20rented%20barrack%20in%20Pune.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20constant%20on%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20chequered%20dining%20tables%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStorytelling%20and%20a%20penchant%20for%20intrepidity%20run%20in%20the%20family%20DNA%2C%20I%20deduce.%20I%E2%80%99m%20listening%20to%20Marzban%E2%80%99s%20tale%20as%20he%20narrates%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F271527%2Fcentury-old-vadilal-ice-cream-brand-first-to-launch-dollies-cones%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat-grandfather%E2%80%99s%20itinerant%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20stories%20are%20juxtaposed%20against%20the%20lores%20of%20the%20Zorastrian%20migration%20following%20the%20Arab%20conquest%20in%20651%20AD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20voice%20assumes%20a%20low%20register%20as%20he%20details%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20escape%20from%20Yazd%20in%20Iran%20to%20Quetta%20(now%20in%20Pakistan)%20to%20Pune%20with%20just%20Rs%2