ipes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccess%20of%20the%20drink%20is%20in%20its%20flavour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Marzban%20points%20out%20that%20much%20before%20sustainability%20was%20the%20buzzword%20it%20is%20now%2C%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20was%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve.%20The%20%E2%80%98returnable%20bottle%E2%80%99%20model%20%E2%80%94%20a%20deposit%20of%20Rs%20360%20is%20charged%20for%20a%20case%20of%2024%20glass%20bottles%20%E2%80%94%20is%20very%20much%20still%20in%20place.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20deposit%20is%20returned%20when%20the%20bottles%20are%20returned%20to%20us%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20customer%20is%20only%20paying%20for%20the%20product.%20That%E2%80%99s%20also%20why%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20retail%20across%20India.%20It%E2%80%99s%20because%2C%20if%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20empty%20bottles%20back%20the%20next%20day%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20anything%20to%20fill%20the%20drinks%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reasons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20success%20reflected%20in%20its%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20retails%20around%20300%20cases%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20fascinating%20how%20an%20unpredictable%20series%20of%20events%20crescendoed%20into%20giving%20Pune%20its%20favourite%20drink.%20But%20as%20Marzban%20emphasises%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20the%20magic%20of%20old-fashioned%20goodness%20in%20a%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750649400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fcarbon-dioxide-1-1750417384.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D452524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20predates%20Coca-Cola%2C%20which%2C%20records%20estimate%20to%20be%20an%20invention%20of%201886%20%E2%80%94%20two%20years%20after%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20started%20in%20a%20small%20rente